Reasoning: 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with control of an ensemble of energy loads, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The energy loads are controlled via coordinated switching, which can be seen as a multi-agent system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a control strategy based on nonlinear feedback, which can be seen as an AI technique. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses a mean field control approach, which can be seen as a machine learning technique. 
- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies): The paper deals with energy loads and their control, which can be seen as an emerging technology.
